<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 18:17:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>万豪表示大中华区预订窗口缩短至三天以内</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/marriott-says-booking-window-greater-china-down-under-three-days-2024-09-05/</link><description>酒店运营商万豪国际集团周四表示，大中华区的一项关键预订指标目前还不到三天，在全球第二大经济体的不确定性不断上升的情况下，人们对旅行计划更加谨慎。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 16:01:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/marriott-says-booking-window-greater-china-down-under-three-days-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦警告终止美国清洁能源税收抵免将增加消费者成本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/yellen-warns-that-ending-us-clean-energy-tax-credits-would-raise-consumer-costs-2024-09-05/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周四警告称，任何取消拜登政府清洁能源税收抵免的企图都会增加家庭成本，并危及正在创造就业机会的美国制造业的新投资。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 15:53:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/yellen-warns-that-ending-us-clean-energy-tax-credits-would-raise-consumer-costs-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>南非总统称中国不会将非洲推入债务陷阱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/china-is-not-pushing-africa-into-debt-trap-south-african-president-says-2024-09-05/</link><description>南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨周四表示，他不认为中国在非洲的投资会将非洲大陆推入“债务陷阱”，而是互利关系的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/china-is-not-pushing-africa-into-debt-trap-south-african-president-says-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国与国际合作伙伴一起对先进技术实施新的控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-implements-new-controls-advanced-technology-alongside-international-partners-2024-09-05/</link><description>美国周四根据国际合作伙伴施加的限制，发布了对包括量子计算机在内的先进技术的新控制措施。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 13:30:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-implements-new-controls-advanced-technology-alongside-international-partners-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲奢侈品股因中国担忧而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/europes-luxury-stocks-drop-china-concerns-2024-09-05/</link><description>欧洲一些大型奢侈品公司的股价周四大幅下跌，交易员称，在世界第二大经济体出现疲软的最新迹象后，人们越来越担心中国主要市场的需求放缓。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 12:49:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/europes-luxury-stocks-drop-china-concerns-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>《资本》报道，德国正在起草针对中国在线折扣店的法规</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/germany-drafting-regulations-chinese-online-discounters-capital-reports-2024-09-05/</link><description>据《资本》杂志报道，德国正在起草新法规，以确保 Temu 和 Shein 等中国折扣零售商遵守产品安全、环境保护、消费者权利以及海关和税法标准。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 11:06:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/germany-drafting-regulations-chinese-online-discounters-capital-reports-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉股价因计划在欧洲和中国推出全自动驾驶而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-gain-plans-launch-full-self-driving-europe-china-2024-09-05/</link><description>特斯拉股价周四上涨逾 6%，此前这家电动汽车制造商坚持其在中国和欧洲推出全自动驾驶 (FSD) 高级驾驶员辅助软件的计划，等待监管机构的批准。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 10:37:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-shares-gain-plans-launch-full-self-driving-europe-china-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>摩根大通以“关税战2.0”风险为由放弃购买中国股票的呼吁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/jpmorgan-ditches-call-buy-chinese-stocks-citing-tariff-war-20-risk-2024-09-05/</link><description>摩根大通放弃了对中国股票的买入建议，警告 11 月美国大选后可能出现第二次关税战的风险，并对中国经济增长表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 08:53:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/jpmorgan-ditches-call-buy-chinese-stocks-citing-tariff-war-20-risk-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚和日本批评中国对菲律宾的“危险”行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-japan-criticise-china-dangerous-acts-towards-philippines-2024-09-05/</link><description>澳大利亚和日本周四批评中国在南海对菲律宾采取“危险和胁迫”行为。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 08:17:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-japan-criticise-china-dangerous-acts-towards-philippines-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促美国“立即”取消对中国商品的所有关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-us-immediately-lift-all-tariffs-chinese-goods-2024-09-05/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，在拜登政府宣布预计对包括电动汽车在内的中国制造的商品加征关税之前，美国应立即取消对中国商品的所有关税。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 07:53:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-us-immediately-lift-all-tariffs-chinese-goods-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，中国因数据、药品进口调查而拘留阿斯利康员工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-detains-astrazeneca-staff-data-drug-import-probes-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-05/</link><description>据彭博社周四援引知情人士的话报道，中国警方拘留了阿斯利康的五名现任和前任员工，对他们可能从事的非法活动进行询问。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 07:25:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-detains-astrazeneca-staff-data-drug-import-probes-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国将对欧盟白兰地进口做出“公平”终裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-make-fair-final-ruling-eu-brandy-imports-2024-09-05/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国将对欧盟进口白兰地作出“客观”、“公正”的终裁。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 07:14:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-make-fair-final-ruling-eu-brandy-imports-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>债权人申请恒大新能源汽车清算</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/creditor-files-liquidation-evergrande-nevs-unit-2024-09-05/</link><description>债权人向上海法院提交了中国恒大新能源汽车集团旗下子公司的破产申请，这是针对这家陷入困境的汽车公司的第三起此类申请。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 06:26:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/creditor-files-liquidation-evergrande-nevs-unit-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>总理表示，尽管中国抗议，马来西亚不会停止南海勘探</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-will-not-stop-south-china-sea-exploration-despite-china-protests-pm-2024-09-05/</link><description>马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣周四表示，尽管北京声称马来西亚侵犯了其领土，但该国不会停止在南海的石油和天然气勘探。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 05:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-will-not-stop-south-china-sea-exploration-despite-china-protests-pm-2024-09-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国向非洲提供510亿美元新资金并承诺提供100万个就业岗位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-deepen-industrial-agricultural-trade-investment-ties-with-africa-2024-09-05/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平周四承诺，中国将在三年内提供近 510 亿美元资金，加大对负债累累的非洲的支持力度，支持更多基础设施项目，并创造至少 100 万个就业岗位。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 02:42:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-deepen-industrial-agricultural-trade-investment-ties-with-africa-2024-09-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>